{{Quote|Our primary task [is] to become the New Republic in fact as well as in name.|[[Mon Mothma/Legends|Mon Mothma]]|<ref name="Dark Force Rising Sourcebook">''[[Dark Force Rising Sourcebook]]''</ref>}}
The '''New Republic Provisional Council''', colloquially known as the '''Rebel Alliance Senate''', was the body of signatories of the [[Declaration of a New Republic/Legends|Declaration of a New Republic]] who served as the government of the fledgling [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] prior to the formation of the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]]. The Council was formed in [[4 ABY/Legends|4.5 ABY]] from the [[Alliance Cabinet/Legends|Alliance Cabinet]] in a [[Constitutional Convention]].

Around [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]], the "Alliance Senate" had taken up its quarters in the [[Palace of the Woolamander]], an ancient [[Massassi/Legends|Massassi]] temple located on the [[Yavin 4/Legends|fourth]] [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Yavin Prime/Legends|Yavin Prime]].<ref name="GoDV" /> It remained mobile until the [[Liberation of Coruscant (Galactic Civil War)|conquest]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] in [[6 ABY/Legends|6.5 ABY]]. Coruscant then became the capital of the New Republic and permanent seat of the New Republic Senate.

Viewed as the government that had [[Second Battle of Coruscant|lost]] Coruscant, the Provisional Council was dissolved after the conclusion of [[Operation Shadow Hand]] and replaced by a [[New Republic Ruling Council|new system]] with a more powerful leader.<ref name="TNEC" />

